<h2>

        The Martian
</h2>

<p>During a manned mission to Mars, astronaut Mark Watney is presumed dead after a fierce storm and is left behind by his crew. But Watney has survived and finds himself stranded and alone on a hostile planet. With only meager supplies, he must utilize his engineering skills, wit, and spirit to subsist and find a way to signal to Earth that he is alive. It is a gripping story of survival, problem-solving, and the resilience of the human spirit against impossible odds.</p></article>
